table>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</table>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<table>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"text-danger\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<b>The medical leave will be considered only if aggregate % is above 75% at the end of semester. Medical leave will be applied between 75% and 85% of attendance with co-curricular</b>\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"text-danger\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<b>The attendance claimed for co-curricular, extra-curricular and departmental activities will  be added to the total aggregate  at the end of semester.</b>\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td >\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<br/>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t* Maximum percentage without leave\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td >\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t* Total Percentage=(Total Class Present/Total Class Conducted)*100\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t <tr>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span>* Value added courses not included</span>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</table>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td width=\"5\" height=\"30\" background=\"images/st_right.gif\"></td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr >\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t   <td width=\"5\" background=\"images/st_left.gif\"></td>\r\n                   \t\t   <td><div align=\"center\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t   <a href=\"javascript:void(0);\" class=\"btn btn-primary\"  onclick=\"printPresentAttendances()\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t     <span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-print\"></span> Print\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t   </a>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t    &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t    <input type=\"button\" name=\"\" value=\"Cancel\" onclick=\"cancelAction()\" class=\"btn btn-primary\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t    </div>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t    </td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t  <td width=\"5\" height=\"30\" background=\"images/st_right.gif\"></td>\r\n                 \t\t</tr>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t <tr>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td height=\"5\"><img src=\"images/st_04.gif\" width=\"5\" height=\"5\" /></td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td background=\"images/st_05.gif\"></td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td><img src=\"images/st_06.gif\" /></td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</table>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<td valign=\"top\" background=\"images/Tright_3_3.gif\" class=\"news\"></td>\r\n\t\t\t\t</tr>\r\n\t\t\t\t<tr>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<td height=\"19\" valign=\"top\" background=\"images/Tright_03_03.gif\"></td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<td valign=\"top\" class=\"news\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<td valign=\"top\" background=\"images/Tright_3_3.gif\" class=\"news\"></td>\r\n\t\t\t\t</tr>\r\n\t\t\t\t<tr>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<td><img src=\"images/st_Tright_03_05.gif\" width=\"9\" height=\"29\"></td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<td width=\"0\" background=\"images/st_TcenterD.gif\"></td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<td><img src=\"images/st_Tright_02.gif\" width=\"9\" height=\"29\"></td>\r\n\t\t\t\t</tr>\r\n\t\t\t</table>\r\n</form>\r\n<script src=\"js/attendance/studentsAttendanceSummary.js?version=1.1\" type=\"text/javascript\"></script>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<!-- Footer  -->\r\n\r\n<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC \"-//W3C//DTD HTML 4.01 Transitional//EN\" \"http://www.w3.org/TR/html4/loose.dtd\">\r\n<html>\r\n<head>\r\n<head>\r\n</head>\r\n<meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=ISO-8859-1\">\r\n\r\n</head>\r\n<body>\r\n<div class=\"footerbottom clearfix\" >\r\n<div class=\"container\">\r\n<div class=\"col-md-8 col-sm-8 link\">\r\n<!--<a href=\"#\">Home</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp